{"tid":2097081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好痴線","createTime":"2020-07-06T14:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T16:16:19.000Z","uid":62948,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1d55bff0f8c06334af33cfdefd387a20193e5661","tid":2097081,"uid":62948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"而家個香港同獨裁地方有得揮，白色恐怖新聞滿天飛，個國安法日日進化嚇鳩你。我睇新聞都驚到想喊。但上黎連登見到大家對住啲新聞一笑置之，玩鬥紅笑返個政府，睇完當堂定左，覺得香港變成點都有你地一齊撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我冇bno，又幾十歲人走唔到，真係好撚灰，但係香港係我屋企，我真係好撚鍾意香港，我唔想走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />移到民既，我祝福你，但你去到邊都好，唔好唔記得呢個屋企。冇得去既，我地一齊圍爐一齊睇住中共點搞死香港，5201314，唔好唔記得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8u8aH2B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8u8aH2B.jpg&h=0f87425f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7516a43818cf59ea6c684c7b5470526e6300c8d1","tid":2097081,"uid":254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"YNWA"},{"pid":"0d450f6613c4bce9a5b1c8d96b6dc56491a1ce1e","tid":2097081,"uid":55080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"本身想正評但見你自己又打5201314<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕甚麼，所以負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2772fbb8c72ad0554faa5f151e65ae677cc858c4","tid":2097081,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"連登一封左就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a949d37e9b2538a83665f3cd1364a03a52908dbc","tid":2097081,"uid":62948,"